{"tid":2053223,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"博爾索納羅批評世衛政治偏頗　揚言巴西將退出組織","createTime":"2020-06-06T05:55:08.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-06T08:51:33.000Z","uid":79563,"like":41,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"22ffb0fe63685ae41613655da0ad4ae75bd9e555","tid":2053223,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-06T05:55:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://newsstatic.rthk.hk/images/mfile_1530530_1_L_20200606114036.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnewsstatic.rthk.hk%2Fimages%2Fmfile_1530530_1_L_20200606114036.jpg&h=cd5713f6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n巴西總統博爾索納羅批評，世界衛生組織是偏頗的政治組織，揚言巴西將退出世衛。<br />\n<br />\n世衛發言人表示，拉丁美洲的新型肺炎疫情令人深切關注。被問到巴西每天的死亡率和確診人數不斷上升時，仍然放寬封鎖措施，發言人表示，解除封鎖措施的其中一個關鍵標準是傳播率下跌。<br />\n<br />\n巴西超過60萬人確診新型肺炎，是全球第二多，累計3萬4千多人死亡，超越意大利，成為死亡病例第三多的國家。博爾索納羅一直反對全面隔離，堅持封鎖經濟比病毒帶來的問題更嚴重。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1530530-20200606.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1530530-20200606.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=bCxsXTpKmrqj5N4FYztdx%2FcTfOzAwtSP2zPdisjLlXU%3D&h=83bb0568\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1530530-20200606.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=5ad5f7e8\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1530530-20200606.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a>"},{"pid":"93adbb12881faf464745d19383d54a490c0f8917","tid":2053223,"uid":143343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-06T05:56:39.000Z","msg":"快退"},{"pid":"ebb5bf1cc08c8fa874d26cc88b1bf58618eff614","tid":2053223,"uid":22736,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-06T05:57:29.000Z","msg":"開始跟隊"},{"pid":"8c7a628aa18080b264e02b51b889ded882692c9b","tid":2053223,"uid":214502,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-06T05:57:53.000Z","msg":"呢條on9<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.